死刑在[[美国|美国]][[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]是一种合法的刑罚。

自1976年以来，该州已经处决了99名被定罪的杀人犯，全都在佛罗里达州立监狱执行。<ref>{{cite web |author=Florida Department of Corrections |url=http://www.dc.state.fl.us/ci/execlist.html |title=Execution List - Florida Department of Corrections |website=Dc.state.fl.us |access-date=2018-11-03 |archive-date=2021-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423035433/http://www.dc.state.fl.us/ci/execlist.html }}</ref>截至2020年11月7日，有339名罪犯等待执行死刑。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dc.state.fl.us/OffenderSearch/deathrowroster.aspx |title=Death Row Roster |website=Dc.state.fl.us |access-date=2017-01-24 |archive-date=2021-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507164154/http://www.dc.state.fl.us/OffenderSearch/deathrowroster.aspx }}</ref>

